iveaux (gènes, espèces, écosystèmes). Un accent est mis sur les enjeux stratégiques que représente la préservation de la biodiversité pour l’avenir de l’humanité.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn French.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 01. Dez 2022) 0aBiodiversity. 0aEvolution (Biology). 4aLife sciences/Biology. 7aSCIENCE / Life Sciences / Biology.2bisacsh1 aGuéguen, Jean-Christophe, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut1 aRioult, Jean-Philippe, eauthor.4aut4http://id.loc.gov/vocabulary/relators/aut08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013z978311102411008iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015z978311075641840uhttps://doi.org/10.1051/978-2-7598-1086-440uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9782759810864423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/document/cover/isbn/9782759810864/original  a978-3-11-075641-8  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2001 - 2015c2001d2015  a978-3-11-102411-0  EDP Sciences Backlist eBook Package 2000-2013c2008d2013  aEBA_BACKALL  aEBA_EBKALL  aEBA_PPALL  aEBA_STMALL  aGBV-deGruyter-alles  aPDA12STME  aPDA5EBK